| [BenchmarkRunner](file:///Users/fahadkiani/Desktop/development/lbx_mcp_universe_template-main/lbx_mcp_universe_cli/lbx_cli/mcpuniverse/benchmark/runner.py#235-578) requires `lbx_cli` in Python path | Import fails in Docker | Set `PYTHONPATH=/app` in Dockerfile + render.yaml |
| MCP server discovery uses relative paths (runner.py:326-334) | Servers not found in Docker | Set `base_dir` explicitly in `CertificationEngine` |
| [config.yaml](file:///Users/fahadkiani/Desktop/development/lbx_mcp_universe_template-main/domains/web_search/config.yaml) uses `type: litellm` for LLM | LLM calls fail without proxy credentials | Override to `type: openai` in the certification service |
| Long benchmark runs (50 tasks × LLM calls) on Render free tier | Render kills process after 15min idle | Use BackgroundTasks + database state + polling fallback |
| WebSocket idle timeout on Render (5 min) | Stream disconnects during run | Client reconnection + polling fallback |
| `!!python/object` YAML deserialization | Full deserialization needs CLI module | Use regex extraction for historical reports |
| SQLite → PostgreSQL migration | Schema differences (JSON vs JSONB) | Use `Text` type consistently (works on both) |
| Concurrent certification runs | Resource contention, OOM | V1: Single-threaded. V2: Celery worker queue |
